  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5adc59cf-54d1-4d6a-9334-03d1faf1bf59\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-91f3d9b4-d26e-4fa6-94fb-39935ccf5309\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d53665df-a163-46a2-afa8-b1d127cd6c95\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3e43e907-2ac4-4360-80aa-a358fbe82a3a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0ac3d83c-68ba-4991-abed-b0daeb9e3b5a\">평일 야간, 일요일 진료가 가능한 이수한의원 입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b404e46d-99c2-4f29-9b81-656511aed1d8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dd3031a5-60cd-4911-ae49-15b6514126f8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0ed36967-aa71-4066-b282-609e253b1bf9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9ffbcf52-2d4b-4dae-9803-1589350d321f\">&quot;원장님, 제 체질은 무엇인가요&quot;</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3179eda6-d79a-4f26-acd7-1c10ef9ca031\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5965574e-ae54-45d9-86ea-20c7962ef89e\">한의원을 방문하는 환자들에게 가장 많이 듣는 질문입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bf54c6f5-862d-4611-abdf-cdb13fb01009\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-28cc0df6-e712-424d-9c40-192317b3ddc3\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c6491335-0115-47d6-8c0b-0030f38afdff\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0174bbba-63d9-419a-85f8-437ff5396f89\">자신의 몸에 맞는 음식과 생활을 하겠다는 거죠.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-00b95a5c-e74c-418a-9c75-2e49983b4432\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0b89bccd-3349-41c0-b7ab-345a56ec4501\">그러나 체질 감별은 두부 자르듯 간단명료하지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ff055cb8-80b1-4d1b-bdbd-98adcb816fae\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a19639b6-8b29-4d6e-bb60-26bc5ee6345c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-086bd37a-ca49-48c5-a333-e204fb548ac5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3be72ca1-a65e-4543-8223-74ac760fecb1\">사상 의학을 창안한 이제마 선생도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5aabad1e-9567-416f-82e5-1bafcf519d06\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ee8ebced-4ea0-432b-8acb-37d7d1a1f530\">감별에 많은 어려움을 느꼈다고 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-eac7cfcd-ad50-4198-a5da-434eadd21810\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-eac7cfcd-ad50-4198-a5da-434eadd21810\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/acc1d8cc236323f6.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1080\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/acc1d8cc236323f6.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/acc1d8cc236323f6.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e7b1ed97-51a5-4beb-93f6-b90de9b4bdd2\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d2767046-35ba-4eee-a335-80bfc6be6af0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-49bff9c3-071a-48da-b9a8-1a936d7d8c59\">&quot;나는 어떤 체질일까?&quot;</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2bb0e36a-daab-4036-a956-23a47180f3aa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f44cd8e8-b451-4a52-bf48-b15539f4192e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ba931572-eaf5-4c2b-b47c-eb2a871d1998\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b6b9f190-7b9d-46eb-a7d6-684fe4e02387\">체질을 확인하기 위해 체형, 성격이나 인상,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b6c2f62f-28f2-4ae6-b41c-e380fa5e67fc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-49a7e81c-bb92-4c88-af8e-b2f6d9219230\">병적 증세, 진맥, 약 처방, 침 치료, 근력 검사 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-95b0668b-183b-4dda-8f6b-e80947409024\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c1fb61fe-f89f-4288-916d-cee3e716da22\">여러 가지 방법이 동원됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9e264662-8f1a-4ab5-b7fa-c2fe4daf02f0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bdd7a6cd-c9db-4684-bf5b-1e750892451a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cfae03f1-cea4-4f90-a598-c3f5624f91b6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-04cb1562-0eac-459e-bde4-dc1c6a63088e\">종합적이고 입체적인 진단과 판단이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ec348970-2386-4a4b-9f9d-88c9faa7140d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-482a7e9b-95db-4e8a-93b4-163ed3a99fde\">필요한 복잡한 과정이죠.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d6097d3b-898e-40b4-a77d-9604f9d375e3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                